<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard Admin - PT Mitrabeton Perkasa</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    
    <style>
        /* ==================== CETAKAN STRUKTUR UTAMA (WAJIB ADA) ==================== */
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f6; display: flex; min-height: 100vh; }
        
        /* INI KUNCI BIAR NGGAK KEPOTONG SIDEBAR */
        .main-content { margin-left: 260px; padding: 40px; width: calc(100% - 260px); box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 100vh; }
        /* =========================================================================== */

        /* ── Topbar Styling ── */
        .topbar { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 30px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .admin-profile { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; background: white; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 30px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); }
        .admin-profile i { color: #334155; font-size: 18px; } /* Warna icon netral untuk Admin */
        /* ========================================================================== */
        
        .btn-logout { background: #fee2e2; color: #dc2626; border-radius: 20px; padding: 6px 15px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; margin-left: 10px; transition: 0.2s; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; }
        .btn-logout:hover { background: #dc2626; color: white; }

        /* ── Dashboard Welcome Card ── */
        .welcome-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #03b426 0%, #3d5450 100%); border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px 45px; color: white; margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.15); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .welcome-text { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
        .welcome-text h3 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .welcome-text p { color: #fcfdfe; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.6; }
        
        .welcome-img { font-size: 120px; color: #38bdf8; opacity: 0.15; position: absolute; right: 40px; top: -10px; z-index: 1; transform: rotate(-10deg); }
        
        .btn-action { background: #fbfcfc; color: #0f172a; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; transition: 0.2s; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3); }
        .btn-action:hover { background: #bfc9ce; color: #0f172a; transform: translateY(-2px); }

        /* ── Quick Stats Grid ── */
        .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .stat-card { background: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; transition: 0.2s; }
        .stat-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        
        .stat-icon { width: 65px; height: 65px; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28px; }
        .bg-blue { background: #e0f2fe; color: #0284c7; }
        .bg-purple { background: #f3e8ff; color: #9333ea; }
        
        .stat-info p { color: #64748b; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 5px 0; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .stat-info h4 { color: #1e293b; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('../partials/sidebar', { role: role }) %>

    <div class="main-content">
        
        <div class="topbar">
            <div class="admin-profile">
                <i class="bi bi-person-circle"></i>
                <%= typeof namaUser !== 'undefined' ? namaUser : 'Administrator' %>
                <span style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 11px; color: #475569; margin-left: 5px;">Admin Master</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="welcome-card">
            <div class="welcome-text">
                <h3>Halo, <%= typeof namaUser !== 'undefined' ? namaUser : 'Super Admin' %>! 👋</h3>
                <p>Selamat datang di panel kontrol utama PT Mitrabeton Perkasa. Dari sini Anda memiliki kendali penuh untuk memantau sistem dan mengelola hak akses seluruh akun karyawan maupun pelanggan.</p>
                
                <a href="/admin/users" class="btn-action">
                    <i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i> Kelola Data Karyawan
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="welcome-img">
                <i class="bi bi-buildings-fill"></i>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-icon bg-blue">
                    <i class="bi bi-person-vcard-fill"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-info">
                    <p>Fungsi Utama</p>
                    <h4>Manajemen Akun</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-icon bg-purple">
                    <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-info">
                    <p>Status Keamanan</p>
                    <h4>Sistem Terlindungi</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>